The pyramid texture of SHJ solar cells presents great anti-reflective performance. The standard apex-angle of pyramid is 70.53°, which is between the (111) surface and the (111¯\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
